Responsibilities for the VP of Data Science: 
Develop and own the Data Governance Framework across a 4,000 person organization 
Drive the adoption of Data Governance practices/program throughout various business units 
Coach business leaders in the understanding of Data Governance processes 
Qualifications for the VP of Data Science: 
10+ years of experience in Data Analytics 
Experience designing/supporting data science strategy 
Deep knowledge of Machine Learning (ML), Artificial Intelligence (AI), and Deep Learning (DL) 
Experience with AWS/Azure
 Thorough understanding of data pipelines, data models, data organization 
Adept at building machine learning and AI models 
Mathematics, probability, statistics expertise
 Experience in financial services, mortgage, lending - ideal 
Compensation/Benefits for the VP of Data Science: 
$180,000 - $190,000 
Restricted Stock Units 
Comprehensive benefit package; Medical, Dental, Vision, 401k, PTO 
Local candidates preferred - remote possible if willing to travel occasionally (Maryland, Philadelphia) 
